{"tid":1083332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣青年炒車跌落15米深山谷 剛好跌落一張舊床褥上保命","createTime":"2019-03-29T14:14:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T14:42:00.000Z","uid":33727,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8ee2d7375694222651f6ae95abb98cb75ed9f9b1","tid":1083332,"uid":33727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T14:14:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20190329/38294494/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fheadline%2Fdaily%2F20190329%2F38294494%2F&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7R5ZC4%2B%2BlHDPeg0yH0hWprM%3D&h=a80935e8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fheadline%2Fdaily%2F20190329%2F38294494%2F&h=caa8fadb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/headline/daily/20190329/38294494/</a><br />\n<br />\n奇蹟 墜15米 跌廢床墊保命 騎士過彎失控 僅輕微骨折<br />\n<br />\n【王智勇╱嘉義報導】高雄一名19歲程姓大學生前天和同學騎機車到嘉義遊玩，一行4人經過嘉義縣中埔鄉台三線幽谷橋附近一處彎道時，騎在最後面的程男突失控，摔落15米深的溪谷，幸運的是，他剛好墜落在一塊廢棄床墊上，撿回一命。搶救的警消說「他真是命大！」<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，前天下午5時許，接獲報案指有人掉落在澐水溪幽谷橋下，趕到後見一男子摔落15公尺深溪谷，人躺在河床石頭上，一旁有一塊廢棄的床墊，男子右腳膝蓋流血受傷；警消出動吊臂搶救，1個多小時後將人吊掛到橋上，經送醫檢查，有骨盆腔輕微骨折及腦震盪現象，生命跡象穩定，現住院治療。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />命不該絕"},{"pid":"0796b670688e57febcdbf94f43eddfb3d3b13845","tid":1083332,"uid":95397,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T14:16:42.000Z","msg":"痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611cac5961b139925f593dd021928d3d461ce9e5","tid":1083332,"uid":95637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T14:23:23.000Z","msg":"天將降大任於斯人也"},{"pid":"9eac414312c50dfae69e1f0137a1980a887321cc","tid":1083332,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T14:42:00.000Z","msg":"Natural selection failed"}]}